      "body": "#### 常用参数"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-31",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "cmake",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "• 方式一: 在`CMakeLists.txt`中使用`set(KEY VAL)`函数\n• 方式二: 在执行`cmake ...` -D<arg> 指定(只需一次,推荐)"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-32",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "cmake",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "cmake",
      "code": "# 指定编译参数(Debug/Release/MinSizeRel/RelWithDebInfo)\n$ cmake ... -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=DEBUG\n# 指定编译链工具(windows下vcpkg需要)\n$ cmake ... -D CMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=<vcpkg_path>/scripts/buildsystems/vcpkg.cmake\n# 指定编译器\n$ cmake ... -D CAMKE_C_COMPILER=...\n$ cmake ... -D CAMKE_CXX_COMPILER=...\n# 指定生成器\n$ cmake .. -G \"Unix Makefile\"\n$ cmake .. -G \"Ninja\"\n$ cmake .. -G \"Visual Studio 17 2022\"\n\n# 设置Cpp标准\nset(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD 17)\nset(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD_REQUIRED ON) # 在检测到不支持时出错\nset(CMAKE_CXX_EXTENSIONS ON) #一般设为off，否则在msvc上没有特性会出错"
    },
